Description:
Classic Hills Home on 1.5 Acres!
This lovely original weatherboard home is located on just over 1.5 acres & comes complete with a brilliant sized pony paddock, 2 dog runs & plenty of space for the kids & animals to play. The home has been recently updated & features 4 spacious bedrooms all with quality carpets & window furnishings & the Master with a split system for added comfort. There are also 2 bathrooms ensuring there is no waiting for a shower, country style kitchen with meals area and gas cooking, large lounge with ambient open fireplace & a spacious second living/dining area with a sunny reading nook. The home has mains gas ducted heating throughout for convenience & features high ceilings, hardwood timber floors & an abundance of natural light reflects off the recently painted contemporary colour scheme. Outside there is a large undercover deck for entertaining that overlooks the rear paddock & distant hills, a 6 car lockable garage, a garden shed, established gardens & ample tank water. If you are looking for a character Hills home with plenty of room for the whole family at a great price this is the one!

Description:
In the Lap (Pool) of Luxury
Take the semi-rural lifestyle to the next level in this beautiful family home. With the local sporting grounds nearby, and situated along the school bus route, family living has never been easier or more luxurious.
Of grand proportions with 4 large bedrooms, gym room / study, including main suite of 5-star proportions, 3 spacious living areas, in-ground, solar heated lap pool with alfresco and triple garage with dual access for recreational vehicle or boat, and every feature has been considered. In winter, snuggle near the fire on the south side of the house, cozy with double-glazed windows admiring the garden. In summer, entertain friends with a view overlooking the pool. Cook together in the large kitchen/family room or relax in the treetops in the upper level balcony overlooking native bush and seasonal creek. Whatever the season, reason, or mood, this home has delivered the invitation to relax and enjoy.
You will want for nothing with fine features throughout including tiled entryway, extra-wide staircase, picture windows, large laundry/wet room, sensor lighting, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, roofline storage, and delightful steel cubby house.
Inspection is sure to impress the most discerning buyers. Plan your viewing today.
- 4 large bedrooms
- Main suite with full ensuite and WIR with dual shower
- 3 living areas
- Lap pool with paved alfresco
- Log fire
- Triple garage with dual access
- Stone bench tops through out
- Vegetable garden, numerous fruit trees
Also visit the stand alone website at: www.5nanganastreetcockatoo.com
Land: 3072 Sq m approx.

COTTAGE CHARACTER, USEABLE BLOCK & A HUGE SHED!!!
This beautifully presented cottage has been lovingly renovated to an exacting standard & offers the lucky purchasers a great opportunity to enjoy all the hard work that has already been done! Originally built in the early 1920's, this home oozes character & charm of days gone by but offers modern luxuries to ensure you will love living here. Boasting high ceilings, ornate cornicing, polished Baltic pine floorboards, modern kitchen with gas, electric & wood stove cooking plus dishwasher, gas ducted heating & split system heating & cooling throughout. Outside you will enjoy landscaped low maintenance cottage gardens, a separate self-contained bungalow with ensuite & 3rd bedroom, a huge 11 x8.5 meter shed (with 3 mt walls) which offers concrete floor, 3 roller doors
& 3 phase power, plus there is a separate outdoor entertaining area or 'man cave' with built in bar & wood fire. There is sealed road access & sealed driveway that leads to a double carport with remote door. Walk to town, transport & sporting facilities - be hurry to inspect, this is a great property!

Description:
THE IDEAL OASIS FOR THE LARGE FAMILY!
Whether you want to get lost amongst the flourishing gardens or watch a movie in the theatre room or relax on the private deck with friends, this property has something for everyone. The home, situated on half an acre walking distance to Cockatoo, features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 4 living areas (including a theatre room), a modern kitchen, an undercover deck for entertaining, a home office with its own entrance & a relaxing rear courtyard. Inside the home has exposed timber ceilings & flows over 4 levels, the Master Suite on the top level offering a sitting area, huge bedroom, a dressing room & spacious ensuite. On the lower level there are 2 further spacious bedrooms with built in robes & their own living space & there is a 4th bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite adjacent to the large lounge room with ambient wood heater, whilst the home has a split system for the warmer days & mains gas ducted heating throughout for the ultimate in comfort. Add to this a modern, well-appointed kitchen with dishwasher, a large dining area, formal entry & plenty of storage throughout the home. Outside there are extensive established gardens with meandering paths, an orchard with a variety of trees, a barn with loft, 3 carports & a concrete drive. If peace, privacy & space are what you seek this could be the one for you!

Description:
SOLID 3 BEDROOM FAMILY HOME ON 3/4 ACRE!
Located privately on of an acre in a sought after pocket of Cockatoo, just a short walk to public transport & the local sports ground, this double brick home with cathedral ceilings features the unique character only found in the Hills. The home offers 3 spacious robed bedrooms, the Master with a walk in robe & ensuite, whilst the family bathroom features a spa, ideal for relaxing away the aches & pains of the day. There is a large, open plan, sunken lounge with an ambient open fire place & a wood heater on the upper level in the family room/dining area overlooking the lounge to keep you warm through the cooler months. Add to this a well-appointed, timber kitchen with convenient island bench with electric cooking, dishwasher & plenty of storage & bench space. The home has a wrap around verandah, mains water & sewer connected, an aviary, a paved garden shed, 500lt water tank for the garden & 1.6 kw solar. All you need do is plan how to make it your own!

Description:
FANTASTIC 6 BEDROOM RESORT STYLE LIVING ON OVER 3 ACRES!
If you love entertaining or simply love having the whole family at home being entertained, this is the home for you. The home features 6 bedrooms with built in robes, Master with walk in robe and ensuite and one of the other 5 bedrooms has a walk in robe also and access to a 3rd bathroom, perfect for the older teenager, guests or even the option of dual accommodation. The living areas are huge, one currently being used as a home theatre with built in sound system, the other has access to a second kitchen. The main kitchen has the home entertainer in mind with quality appliances, sleek black stone bench tops and gloss black cupboards- it definitely has the wow factor. There is direct access from the kitchen to the outdoor decked, undercover entertaining area, perfect for family and friends to gather all year round. Outside there is a fenced outdoor spa and in ground swimming pool surrounded by tropical landscaped gardens, a double carport 2 double lockup garages and under house storage. There is plenty of space for 4 legged friends and for the kids to run and ride their bikes. This is the perfect house for the larger family or families who like their space.
